OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill see a few showers. Then the rest
OL,7,Fof the night will be mainly dry with
OL,8,Fvariable amounts of cloud. Cold with
OL,9,Fsome frost.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FDry in the morning before
OL,12,Foutbreaks of rain spread east across
OL,13,Fall parts in the afternoon and evening.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCloudy
OL,16,Fon Friday with some showery rain.
OL,17,FCloudy on Saturday with rain, heavy at
OL,18,Ftimes, spreading east, severe gales
OL,19,Fpossible.. Cold and bright on Sunday
OL,20,Fwith blustery showers.
